(1) Cholinesterase inhibitor — rivastigmine (best evidence) or donepezil — may improve cognition + reduce hallucinations + behavior;

(2) AVOID typical antipsychotics + most atypicals (severe neuroleptic sensitivity → worsen parkinsonism, NMS, sudden death):
