(5) Address comorbid AD pathology (mixed dementia very common — most 'pure' vascular has AD component);

(6) Fall prevention (gait, urinary urgency);

(7) Caregiver education + support;

(8) Advance planning + safety + driving assessment;

(9) Long-term: progressive — stepwise (vascular events) or gradual (small vessel disease);

(10) Multidisciplinary: neurology, primary care, geriatric, PT/OT, social work, caregiver;

