Psychotropic Medication Monitoring:

(1) Antipsychotics — atypical metabolic monitoring (APA/ADA consensus):
  • Baseline: weight + BMI + waist circumference, BP, HbA1c or fasting glucose, fasting lipid panel, personal + family hx CV/DM;
  • Follow-up: weight + BP at 4, 8, 12 wk, then quarterly; HbA1c + lipids at 12 wk, then annually;
